Platform
The Imperial Nationalist Party (INP) is built on the bedrock of six things. Fatherland, Family, Tradition, Work, Empire, and Sovereignty. These core tenants of our ideology is what we believe as the only way white western civilization can be preserved and expanded.

Some of our beliefs:

- No LGBTQ+ - penalties are either expulsion or death

- Mandatory military service of 2 years for 18 year old males

- Only right wing parties in government

- A mix of authoritarian and democracy for governmental structure: Mosleyist style of government

- Citizens are free to bear arms

- Free enterprise and private property limited to the nations citizens and only to foreigners of ethnically similar and pure blood.

- Ethnically based economy

- Capitalism (In it's purer laizefare form) is accepted and practiced as the economic engine of our ideology.

- We see the rest of the world as ours to conquer and govern as we see fit for the betterment of the white race.

- Blood and soil environmentalism: (preserving the purity of the race & protecting the environment that our race was raised on

- Protection of natural beauty and historical monuments

- Voting is restricted to minimum age of 25, must be father of household and own land.

- The only tax is on vice and property

- Foreign investment/capital is tolerable under certain conditions. Foreigners may not own residential land or utilities. For everything else (Companies/Commercial land & buildings) foreigners may only own up to 50% of what ever they are putting their money into, the labor must be sourced locally, and the profits must stay within the state. They can leave with their original capital however they may not pull money out of our nation

- Pro-life

- Physical fitness is a requirement.

- Führerprinzip is followed in the political party.

- Education is carried out/handled by the private sector. The only interference government has with education is to economically benefit (tax breaks/incentives) those schools which perform in the upper tiers of education by producing the most educated and well rounded students.

- A standing military force will present at all times.

- Anti Marxist/communist/socialist.

- Actively practice eugenics to improve the gene pool of our nation.

- Children in kindergarten must be taught and be able to read Mein Kampf from cover to cover.  
